videos.headline: Nothern Illinois QB throws dime for 14-yard TD
videos.description: Marcus Childers finds Spencer Tears on the double-move, giving the Huskies a 7-3 lead.

videos.headline: Huskies QB completes second TD pass of 1st half
videos.description: Marcus Childers throws a dart to WR Dennis Robinson for a 7-yard touchdown, extending Northern Illinois' lead to 14-3.

videos.headline: Central Michigan narrows lead with 6-yard QB draw
videos.description: QB Tommy Lazzaro keeps it himself and powers his way across the goal-line, cutting the Huskies' lead to 21-10.

videos.headline: Chippewas come within striking distance on 4-yard TD pass
videos.description: QB Tommy Lazzaro throws a strike to WR Julian Hicks, bringing Central Michigan to within 5.
